Recommends: openssl
Description: H3C firewall syslog to SGBox SIEM translator
 Receives TLS/TCP syslog messages from H3C Comware firewalls,
 translates the proprietary key(id)=value format into clean
 key=value pairs, and forwards them to SGBox SIEM.
 .
 Features:
  - Fully async (aiohttp + uvloop)
  - TLS 1.2+ enforcement on all listeners
  - REST API with authentication, rate limiting, and IP whitelist
  - Structured JSON logging via structlog
  - Pull mode (SGBox connects) and push mode (translator forwards)
  - Systemd service with security hardening
